Solution Design 

Approach 
The solution is designed as a backend integration layer between onboarding requests and DocuSign. 
 The service receives employee information, evaluates business rules, creates a signing workflow, and tracks document status. 

Workflow 
HR System / API Request → Backend Service → Business Rule Evaluation → DocuSign Envelope Creation → Status Tracking 

