Components 
API Layer: Receives onboarding requests. 
Business Logic Layer: Determines recipient routing based on employee level. 
DocuSign Service: Handles authentication and envelope creation. 
DocuSign Rest API: create and send envelope 
Docuisgn Status API: tracks envelope status 

Design Decision 
Business rules are handled inside the integration layer rather than inside DocuSign. 
 This makes workflow updates easier to maintain. 

